{"tid":1725164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到因中大物資鬧分化，聽小弟講兩句","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T01:26:59.000Z","uid":8011,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"09811398b4d225c7f283909be83fa17f5e5c3fee","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"關於好多物資包括食物同裝備被遺棄中大，糟蹋捐贈者心意。<br />\n<br />\n香港人黃絲力量團結的精神底下，一方有難，馬上八方支援，各位一呼百應，有備無患送左好多物資上來，係因為唔知中大呢一役要守要幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n以一般人心態去理解，我覺得，<br />\n由於中大手足/同學緊急疏散要離開中大，造成物資遺棄有以下猜測：<br />\n<br />\n魔法：和理非唔敢拎/  勇武手足拎唔到咁多<br />\n<br />\n食物：唔值錢，所以唔係首要拎。其實可以第日再返去執返d食物，有用的分發比人或者送去canteen廚房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不完美，可改善，<br />\n唔好分化和理非同勇武，大家好需要大家。互相支持先可以令運動成功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 非中大人，有錯請指正。"},{"pid":"24ff486b815e5906d5135139038427647a6db336","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"348d613336859e815abd244b18053f6a3ae50699","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:19:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"622985f121f36c8ce54dc7db741389f846b55bc3","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"3連"},{"pid":"133dc1721e1caee3ac0d05ef793a1f6878c5804c","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:19:33.000Z","msg":"4連"},{"pid":"181971b7062eb517acb67a6f826f43cb7de3bad7","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"5大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"68bbeb101c2b682bf671bae5dd21cf27bfe182be","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"6年"},{"pid":"5ca9a5db0d2714eaa040695d1c3837c08948e6f9","tid":1725164,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"柒婆死全家"},{"pid":"352b9d22dbcbfde1a3b5fef10fc2ae09f3aa9bda","